metadata.name: The Yellow Buick
metadata.description:
'The Yellow Buick' was photographed and thoughtfully selected as one of two pieces in the genesis collection of photographer Judith Ragg also known as Lekapie. 

This pieces includes both a 1/1 NFT and a physical counterpart that is available as a package deal to its collector at primary sale.

The other piece in this genesis collection is 'The Yellow Bambina'
